-- Lakshmi Vilas in Talks With Citigroup to Buy Financing Unit, E.Times Says
-- Victoria Batchelor
-- 2010-07-22T23:52:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/lakshmi-vilas-in-talks-with-citigroup-to-buy-financing-unit-e-times-says.html

          
          
             Lakshmi Vilas Bank Ltd. is in talks
with Citigroup Inc. to acquire CitiFinancial Consumer Finance
India, a company that provides retail loans to low-income
borrowers, the Economic Times reported, citing an unidentified
person familiar with the proposal. Lakshmi Vilas hired JM
Financial Ltd. to carry out due diligence on the business,
according to the report.  
          
          


  


        